<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#098658;--shiki-dark:#B5CEA8;">5</span><span style="--shiki-light:#000000;--shiki-dark:#D4D4D4;">. Cross-Worker Synchronization: Initial state synchronization occurs</span></span>
